led with no memory of what happened. You play as Realm, a simple peasant, who's goal is to lift the curse. Only you remember what happened between each reset. Learn, adapt, slay beasts, find loot, die, rinse and repeat!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Solo Developer:</strong></h2>Made by one dude! Join the discord, ask me anything, leave me suggestions and feedback!<br>",
